  "texts": [
    "Our framework consists of an ECoG decoder that maps the ECoG signals to interpretable acoustic speech parameters (for example, pitch, voicing and formant frequencies), as well as a speech synthesizer that translates the speech parameters to a spectrogram.",
    "The speech synthesizer is differentiable, enabling us to minimize the spectrogram reconstruction error during training of the ECoG decoder.",
    "The low-dimensional latent space, together with guidance on the latent representation generated by a pre-trained speech encoder, overcomes data scarcity issues.",
    "Our publicly available framework produces naturalistic speech that highly resembles the speaker's own voice, and the ECoG decoder can be realized with different deep learning model architectures and using different causality directions.",
    "We report this"
  ],
